<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَبِإِيجَابٍ وَقَبُولٍ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>-<span class="c5"> بِسَبْعَةِ شُرُوطٍ:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> الرِّضَا مِنْهُمَا.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَكَوْنُ عَاقِدٍ جَائِزَ التَّصَرُّفِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[٣]</span> وَكَوْنُ مَبِيعٍ مَالاً.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَهُوَ:</span> مَا فِيهِ مَنْفَعَةٌ مُبَاحَةٌ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c4">[٤]</span> وَكَوْنُهُ مَمْلُوكاً لِبَائِعِهِ، أَوْ مَأْذُوناً لَهُ فِيهِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c4">[٥]</span> وَكَوْنُهُ مَقْدُوراً عَلَى تَسْلِيمِهِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c4">[٦]</span> وَكَوْنُهُ مَعْلُوماً لَهُمَا:<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
